data.description: Charming ~782 sqft 2 bed 1 bath Craftsman in wonderful Olympia neighborhood! Situated in a quiet location yet close to Farmers Market, Children's Museum, Bigelow Park, and tons of other amenities. Inside, you will find two nicely sized bedrooms, a full bath, spacious living room and kitchen with connected dining space and utility room. This home offers a  fully fenced  back yard with additional side yard, an outbuilding for tools/storage, and a covered front porch to enjoy all year long. Don't miss the chance to make this property your own; schedule a showing today to explore all it has to offer!
